          "literature": [],
          "nodes": [],
          "patches": []
        },
        "body": "# Abstract\nOld.\n# Introduction\nOld.\n# Methods\nOld.\n# Results\nThe fit slope is 2.0.\n# Discussion\nOld.\n# Limitations\nOld.\n# References\nNone.",
